<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background: #50b3a2;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }
        .profile-picture {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        }
        .bio {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .skills, .hobbies {
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        .skills ul, .hobbies ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .skills li, .hobbies li {
            background: #e2e2e2;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Me</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="profile.jpg" alt="Profile Picture" class="profile-picture">
        <div class="bio">
            <h2>John Doe</h2>
            <p>Hello! I'm John, a web developer with a passion for creating interactive and dynamic web applications. I have a strong background in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and I love learning new technologies and improving my skills.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skills">
            <h3>Skills</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>HTML & CSS</li>
                <li>JavaScript</li>
                <li>React.js</li>
                <li>Node.js</li>
                <li>Python</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="hobbies">
            <h3>Hobbies</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Reading</li>
                <li>Traveling</li>
                <li>Photography</li>
                <li>Coding</li>
                <li>Gaming</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
